OL,4,Cmurdered outside nightclub
OL,6,FITV News' Kathy Wardle spoke Mike's
OL,7,Ffamily about their hopes for the trust.
OL,9,FThe family of a man who was killed
OL,10,Foutside a nightclub in Bodmin have
OL,11,Fbeen holding a fundraiser to raise
OL,12,Fawareness of knife crime.
OL,14,FMIKES Trust was set up in memory of
OL,15,FMichael Riddiough-Allen, who died
OL,16,Fafter being stabbed outside the
OL,17,FEclipse nightclub in April last year.
