OL,6,FOn Sunday 23 June, thousands gathered
OL,7,Fin Perranporth Airfield for MIKES
OL,8,FMotor Mania, a fundraising event to
OL,9,Fhonour his love of cars.
OL,11,FMichael's younger sister Alicia Puckey
OL,12,Fsays the family hope to fund youth
OL,13,Fclubs and community groups to give
OL,14,Fyoung people positive places to go.
OL,16,FAlicia said: "We're focussing on
OL,17,Fsupporting youth groups and giving
OL,18,Feverybody the chance to be part of a
OL,19,Fyouth group and find their passion.
