OL,3,CMotor event held in memory of man
OL,4,Cmurdered outside nightclub
OL,6,F"If they are part of a rugby team, or
OL,7,Fa darts team or the arts, and if they
OL,8,Fhave that support network, they are
OL,9,Fless likely to go down the wrong path
OL,10,Fwhich could end up with them carrying
OL,11,Fa knife."
OL,13,FKevin Allen, Michael's dad, said:
OL,14,F"This event is to reflect Mike's
OL,15,Fpassions and the friendship that
OL,16,Fexisted between all the people within
OL,17,Fthe car group who were incredibly hard
OL,18,Fhit by the loss of Mike.
