OL,3,CMotor event held in memory of man
OL,4,Cmurdered outside nightclub
OL,6,F"He was a big character, always
OL,7,Fhelping people, always helpful. Not
OL,8,Fonly is MIKES Motor Mania a part of
OL,9,Four family journey in terms of grief,
OL,10,Fbut also the wider car family journey
OL,11,Fof celebrating a young life lost."
OL,13,FIn April this year, 25-year-old Jake
OL,14,FHill was jailed for life for Michael's
OL,15,Fmurder and for injuring four others.
OL,17,FMichael had been an innocent bystander
OL,18,Fwho had tried to stop Hill's rampage
OL,19,Foutside the Eclipse club in April 2023.
